      • satisfiedBy

        boolean satisfiedBy(Lang other)
        Is this Lang satisfied by another Lang. If the other lang defines a country code, then this is equivalent to equals, if it doesn't, then the equals is only done on language and the country of this lang is ignored.

        This implements the language matching specified by RFC.2616 Section 14.4. Equality is case insensitive as per Section 3.10.

        Parameters:
        other - Another Lang
        Returns:
        true if is this Lang is satisfied by the other Lang
